def getData(arr):
    lst=list()
    for i in range(arr.shape[0]):#browse the row
        for j in range(arr.shape[1]):##browse the column
            lst.append(array[i,j])#add data to the list
    return lst

def magic(array):
    trace=trace(array)
    mat=np.fill(array.shape,trace)
    row_sum_mat=np.sum(axis=1)
    col_sum_mat=np.sum(axis=0)
    return mat==row_sum_mat==col_sum_mat
